A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Utilities – Solar Energy Generating Systems – Floating Systems and
3 Systems Located on Brownfields
4 FOR the purpose of providing that certain floating solar energy generating systems are
5 eligible for the Small Solar Energy Generating System Incentive Program;
6 exempting certain floating solar energy generating systems and solar energy
7 generating systems located on brownfields from a certain property tax; and generally
8 relating to solar energy generating systems.
